summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over a portion of South Findlay Street in the plat of Commercial Street Steam Motor Addition, and over a portion of 37th Avenue East as platted in the Replat of John J. McGilvra's 3rd Addition for storm drain and sanitary sewer purposes. (Street Vacation, South Findlay Street - C.F. 282902; and Street Vacation, 37th Avenue East - C.F. 281871).
